  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Let's start from scratch...\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scritchy Scratchy is a super-satisfying scratch card incremental game where luck is your weapon, and glittering riches are just a scratch away.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a growing collection of scratchers, each with its own quirks, surprises, and sometimes downsides. Rip through tickets, uncover rare symbols, tweak your own luck, and chase absurd payouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Scratch Bot, your tireless mechanical friend who scratches and reveals the rewards for you. Turn your run into a full-blown jackpot engine as your balance shoots through the roof while you sit back and relax.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"A series of bouncing scratch cards.\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Scratch. Upgrade. Repeat.\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you prosper, you’ll unlock upgrades that twist luck in your favor:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Boosted odds and payouts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Faster and easier scratching </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• New scratch card variants with unique rules</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But power always comes with risk. Some cards tempt you with monstrous payouts at the cost of nasty penalties. Some offer steady income… others threaten your entire run. Will you play like a sensible adult or gamble like a degenerate in a neon casino?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Multiple scratch cards being scratched.\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.mp4?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"To the moon!\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you’re ready for even more madness, Prestige to reset your run, gather Jack Points, and spend them on permanent upgrades that reshape your strategy. Build your own luck engine: Slow and steady, wildly explosive, or pure chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scritchy Scratchy is a dangerously satisfying progression casino, where every scratch is a little dopamine hit, and every run is one lucky break away from the big jackpot!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Let's start from scratch...\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fab6df7767e6384fcaf9dcecd27efa44.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Scritchy Scratchy is a super-satisfying scratch card incremental game where luck is your weapon, and glittering riches are just a scratch away.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into a growing collection of scratchers, each with its own quirks, surprises, and sometimes downsides. Rip through tickets, uncover rare symbols, tweak your own luck, and chase absurd payouts.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock Scratch Bot, your tireless mechanical friend who scratches and reveals the rewards for you. Turn your run into a full-blown jackpot engine as your balance shoots through the roof while you sit back and relax.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"A series of bouncing scratch cards.\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/fdf689d4fafe4ee00eb599a220608ebc.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Scratch. Upgrade. Repeat.\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/e4c6c7305f500d246e41db1d3d0c43d2.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As you prosper, you’ll unlock upgrades that twist luck in your favor:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Boosted odds and payouts</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• Faster and easier scratching </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• New scratch card variants with unique rules</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But power always comes with risk. Some cards tempt you with monstrous payouts at the cost of nasty penalties. Some offer steady income… others threaten your entire run. Will you play like a sensible adult or gamble like a degenerate in a neon casino?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"Multiple scratch cards being scratched.\" width=780 height=380 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/3727db2d3c357cc693037794f20d5035.mp4?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.poster.avif?t=1773831686\" aria-label=\"To the moon!\" width=780 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3948120/extras/432c130a7bc4d83bd29bb6bc0d345058.webm?t=1773831686\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you’re ready for even more madness, Prestige to reset your run, gather Jack Points, and spend them on permanent upgrades that reshape your strategy. Build your own luck engine: Slow and steady, wildly explosive, or pure chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Scritchy Scratchy is a dangerously satisfying progression casino, where every scratch is a little dopamine hit, and every run is one lucky break away from the big jackpot!</p>",
